  <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">DFT study of the structural transformations and absorption properties of crystalline 2,6-dimethyl-4-(diphenylmethylene)-2,5-cyclohexadienone under hydrostatic compression</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="260" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
